Package: ContinentalTesting
Type: Package
Title: Test continental DAISIE MLE model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
             given = "Joshua W.", 
             family = "Lambert", 
             email = "j.w.lambert@rug.nl", 
             role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5218-3046")
           )
Description: A set of functions and scripts to analyse the continental 
    (non-oceanic) DAISIE model of island biogeography. The package contains
    analysis and plotting scripts to determine the precision, reliability and 
    bias of inferring vicariant species from phylogenetic island community data.
